You can target 1 "Superheavy Samurai" monster you control; equip this monster from your hand or your side of the field to that monster you control. Once per turn, the monster equipped with this card by this effect cannot be destroyed by card effects. When a Defense Position monster is destroyed by battle and sent to your Graveyard: You can send this card from your hand to the Graveyard; Special Summon that monster in Attack Position.
